## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-317">`WriteEvent`方法提供了具有字符串和整数自变量组合的重载。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-317">The `WriteEvent` method provides overloads with combinations of string and integer arguments.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-318">如果没有这些组合匹配调用的参数，编译器将使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>重载，这是比其他重载慢得多。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-318">If none of these combinations match the parameters for the call, the compiler uses the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> overload, which is considerably slower than the other overloads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-319">请参阅重载页面了解详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-319">See the overload page for details.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-320">在所有情况下，`eventid`参数应为大于 0 或小于 65535 或可以操作中发生错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-320">In all cases, the `eventid` parameter should be greater than 0 or less than 65535 or errors can occur in the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-321">如果出现错误，请执行您可以通过检查的输出流的调试器，获取有关错误的源的详细信息，如果您有一个调试器附加到触发事件的过程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-321">If errors do occur, you can get more information about the source of the error by checking the output stream of the debugger, if you have a debugger attached to the process firing events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-322">如果发生错误的事件源中有的 ETW 侦听器，还可以查看 ETW 事件流，以报告的错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-322">You can also look for errors reported in the ETW event stream, if you have an ETW listener on the event source where the error occurs.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-323">当实现标识为中的 ETW 事件方法<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-派生的类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-323">When you implement a method that is identified as an ETW event in an <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-derived class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-324">必须调用基类<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>方法并传递<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A>和实现的方法类似于下面的示例相同的参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-324">You must call the base class <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> method passing the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A> and the same arguments as the implemented method similar to the following example.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[Event(2, Level = EventLevel.Informational)]  
public void Info1(string arg1)  
{  
 base.WriteEvent(2, arg1);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d31d9-325">此外可以通过创建自定义重载<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d31d9-325">You can also create a custom overload by using the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A> method.</span></span>

  
  
